Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • fc.Manager

  • public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    A Manager is a class that wraps all the others. It reads the input file, writes in the tree, modifies the tree and writes in the output file.
    Author:
    Laurent Fite
